Defines the most popular GENTOO_MIRRORS setting throughout the
administrative realm, enabling multiple sites to use them
as a shared patch.

Index: etc/make.conf
===================================================================
--- etc.orig/make.conf
+++ etc/make.conf
@@ -598,4 +598,4 @@ SSL_UNIT="Preliminary usage"
 # This will typically be the /usr/portage/distfiles directory of some
 # other machine, exported as a network share.
 #
-#GENTOO_MIRRORS=""
+GENTOO_MIRRORS="/usr/portage/local/distfiles/local /usr/portage/local/distfiles /usr/portage/local/distfiles/precious /usr/portage/local/distfiles/mnt http://mirrors.evolva.ro/gentoo/ ftp://mirrors.evolva.ro/gentoo/ ftp://ftp.join.uni-muenster.de/pub/linux/distributions/gentoo ftp://gentoo.chem.wisc.edu/gentoo/ ftp://gentoo.mirrors.tds.net/gentoo http://gentoo.in.th/ http://gentoo.mirrors.tds.net/gentoo ftp://gentoo.in.th/ ftp://ftp.twaren.net/Linux/Gentoo/ ftp://ftp.join.uni-muenster.de/pub/linux/distributions/gentoo"
